wiki.text:
'WTD' is a three-letter abbreviation with multiple meanings, as described below:

*Working Time Directive - a collection of regulations concerning hours of work
*Water Tight Door - United States Navy *What To Do - An expression for
confusion and uncertainty *The World Taxonomist Database *What the Dickens - a
minced oath, with 'Dickens' standing for devil *What the Duck - an online comic
strip by Aaron Johnson *Win the Day - a favorite phrase among Oregon Ducks
football fans
* World Toilet Day, see World Toilet Organization#World Toilet Day
